Mountains allow different segments
of etheric plane(from underworld
caves to top of Sumeru) to interface
with physical world: the 
mountain air is infused with ether
and cosmic energy, compared to
shielded surface Earth.

Mountains are most complex
spiritual environment category
as they can contain all elemental
configurations of areas and
interface different 'elemental
 flows', being a etheric gateway
space with powerful energy flows
from weather systems, telluric
currents and underworld energies
to water streams and volcanic eruptions..
